@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_kqtgma(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos((wp.cos(v2 + 0.47) / wp.abs(v0 + 0.86)))
    tmp = wp.sin(0.86)
    v1 = (0.11 + v0)
    v2 = (0.38 * (wp.cos(tmp + 0.82) / 0.14))
    data[tid] = v0
